data.description: Updated 3 bedroom home in the Oxford School District only 2 miles from Kroger and 3 miles to the Square.  Wood floors in main living areas and bedrooms.  Large, 2 car garage leads to an oversize laundry/mud room.  Metal roof, brick and siding exterior provide a durable, low maintenance home that is move in ready!  Come see it before it's gone.
